      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/ea666f/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2025-02-12T07:54:31.674Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Ok, It worked out\u2026 sort of.</p>\n<p>Here\u2019s what I did:</p>\n<p>Completely erased and reinstalled TD<br>\nUpdated my S24<br>\nReset my Elite Direto through its app<br>\nEdge shut off, no ANT+ dongle attached</p>\n<p>The trainer finally appeared in TD and connected normally. But\u2026</p>\n<p>As soon as I started the workout, I got these crazy power numbers:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/e/e0819a2976e9eeb84869352bcc35a9fb4b3ef945.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/e0819a2976e9eeb84869352bcc35a9fb4b3ef945\" title=\"Screenshot_20250212_050705_TrainerDay\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e0819a2976e9eeb84869352bcc35a9fb4b3ef945_2_230x500.jpeg\" alt=\"Screenshot_20250212_050705_TrainerDay\" data-base62-sha1=\"w24CJK5UH6ENvj0VeRP8zrDdhaJ\" width=\"230\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e0819a2976e9eeb84869352bcc35a9fb4b3ef945_2_230x500.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e0819a2976e9eeb84869352bcc35a9fb4b3ef945_2_345x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e0819a2976e9eeb84869352bcc35a9fb4b3ef945_2_460x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"2C334B\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot_20250212_050705_TrainerDay</span><span class=\"informations\">1080\u00d72340 150 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Restarted again and it began to work but my Garmin HRM-Dual was gone after a while, though it was showing as connected:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/7/7668c8496ecb2d0584e18308513142e018b6f0ab.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/7668c8496ecb2d0584e18308513142e018b6f0ab\" title=\"Screenshot_20250212_065931_TrainerDay\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/7668c8496ecb2d0584e18308513142e018b6f0ab_2_230x500.jpeg\" alt=\"Screenshot_20250212_065931_TrainerDay\" data-base62-sha1=\"gTuPSiz6yZI5jhT0INOuDBDjqST\" width=\"230\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/7668c8496ecb2d0584e18308513142e018b6f0ab_2_230x500.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/7668c8496ecb2d0584e18308513142e018b6f0ab_2_345x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/7668c8496ecb2d0584e18308513142e018b6f0ab_2_460x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"2B3041\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot_20250212_065931_TrainerDay</span><span class=\"informations\">1080\u00d72340 147 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/f/f3b506889cd1d3a8919ef267fd3214325e11ddcb.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/f3b506889cd1d3a8919ef267fd3214325e11ddcb\" title=\"Screenshot_20250212_070053_TrainerDay\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f3b506889cd1d3a8919ef267fd3214325e11ddcb_2_230x500.jpeg\" alt=\"Screenshot_20250212_070053_TrainerDay\" data-base62-sha1=\"yLVRZ0TNcCCcvVThiC2tJEV8bvd\" width=\"230\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f3b506889cd1d3a8919ef267fd3214325e11ddcb_2_230x500.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f3b506889cd1d3a8919ef267fd3214325e11ddcb_2_345x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f3b506889cd1d3a8919ef267fd3214325e11ddcb_2_460x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"24252D\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot_20250212_070053_TrainerDay</span><span class=\"informations\">1080\u00d72340 148 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>At the end of the day, not the most stable setup, but it kind of works.</p>",
