      "created_at": "2025-02-14T12:58:24.928Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Yes, Wahoo and Tacx Neo are rock solid from my perspective.  I even had a Neo 1 that I left outside for 3 years and training on the terrace and it never died\u2026 I don\u2019t ride that much, mostly testing instead of longer training but still\u2026  Also our customers with Wahoo or Neo are rarely the trainer problem (maybe multiple apps connected or something else) or in rare cases something we need to fix, but we have not heard of anything in a while.  Elite seems good but for sure temperamental.</p>",
