      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/ea666f/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2025-02-14T14:24:30.946Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Maybe\u2026 I found a startup procedure that makes Direto and TD go along well. Have to test it again and again. I\u2019ll let you know.</p>",
