      "name": "dermate",
      "username": "dermate",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/ea666f/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2025-02-16T08:53:41.639Z",
      "cooked": "<p>And here I am. Just got the latest TD update.<br>\nThe procedure to make TD and Direto talk \u201cseamlessly\u201d sounds tricky but kinda works.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Power on your Direto</li>\n<li>Open TD app</li>\n<li>Wait for Direto and TD to connect via BLE (after a few seconds, you can actually hear DIreto hanshaking)</li>\n<li>Power on your Garmin Edge and wait it to connect to Direto via ANT+</li>\n<li>Exit TD and re-open it (usually this step is required, but every now ad then not\u2026).</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Garmin Edge connection is mandatory since TD is not recording essential training data (CORE temp, etc.).</p>\n<p>Maybe it helps.</p>",
      "post_number": 14,
      "post_type": 1,
      "updated_at": "2025-02-16T08:53:41.639Z",
