      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/ea666f/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2025-02-17T08:58:14.247Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Yes of course it\u2019s not paired as \u201ctrainer\u201d: it only reads data as the Direto power meter is seen as a simple sensor.</p>\n<p>The issue of TD (restart it multiple times before it gets the connection right) is seen with other trainers, I see in this forum.</p>",
